      <title>西波隆称欧洲央行应进一步降息以支持经济复苏</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/ecb-should-cut-rates-further-support-recovery-cipollone-says-2024-11-15/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[欧洲央行执委会委员皮耶罗·西波洛内周五表示，欧洲央行应进一步降息，以支持欧元区刚刚起步的经济复苏，同时也要面对美国可能征收的新贸易关税。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/markets/rates-bonds/ecb-should-cut-rates-further-support-recovery-cipollone-says-2024-11-15/</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 15 Nov 2024 16:16:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
