      <title>百时美施贵宝因抗癌药物延期上市再次面临 67 亿美元诉讼</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/legal/bristol-myers-faces-renewed-67-bln-lawsuit-over-delayed-cancer-drug-2024-11-14/</link>
